file.name: openapi-schema.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: ''
  version: ''
paths:
  /account/states/:
    get:
      operationId: listStates
      description: ''
      parameters: []
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: &id001
                type: array
                items:
                  properties:
                    id:
                      type: integer
                      readOnly: true
                    name:
                      type: string
                      maxLength: 50
                    shortcode:
                      type: string
                      maxLength: 2
                  required:
                  - name
                  - shortcode
            text/html:
              schema: *id001
          description: ''
  /account/subjects/:
    get:
      operationId: listSubjects
      description: ''
      parameters: []
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: &id002
                type: array
                items:
                  properties:
                    id:
                      type: integer

                      maxLength: 50
                  required:

            text/html:
              schema: *id002
          description: ''
  /account/schooltypes/:
    get:
      operationId: listSchoolTypes

      parameters: []

        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: &id003
                type: array
                items:
                  properties:

                  required:

          description: ''

                    grade:

                    school_type:
                      type: integer

                  - school_type
            text/html:
              schema: *id004
          description: ''
  /account/schooldata/{school_type}/:

        required: true

        '200':

            application/json:

                  uuid:
                    type: string

                    readOnly: true
                  first_name:
                    type: string
                    maxLength: 50
                  state:
                    type: integer
                  studentdata:
                    properties:
                      school_data:
                        type: integer

                    - school_data
                    type: object
                  tutordata:
                    properties:
                      schooldata:
                        type: array
                        items:
                          type: integer
                      subjects:
                        type: array
                        items:
                          type: integer
                      profile_picture:
                        type: string
                        format: binary
                        nullable: true
                    required:
                    - schooldata
                    - subjects
                    type: object

                    enum:

                    - FE
                    - DI
                required:

                - state

                      subjects:

                        items:

                  type: string
                  maxLength: 50

                  type: string
                  maxLength: 50

                  - FE
                  - DI
                state:
                  type: integer
                password:
                  type: string

                    school_data:
                      type: integer

                  type: object
                  nullable: true
                tutordata:

                    subjects:

                      items:
                        type: integer
                    verification_file:

                    verified:
                      type: boolean

                    profile_picture:
                      type: string

                  - subjects

                      subjects:

                      verified:

                        readOnly: true
                      profile_picture:
                        type: string
                        format: binary
                        nullable: true
                    required:

                    - subjects
                    type: object
                    nullable: true

                - gender

                  maxLength: 254
                first_name:
                  type: string

                state:
